==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Summoner
<hw>Sum"mon*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>somner</ets>, <ets>sompnour</ets>, OF. <ets>semoneor</ets>, F.
<ets>semonneur</ets>. See <er>Summon</er>, <pos>v. t.</pos>]</ety>
<def>One who summons; one who cites by authority; specifically, a petty
officer formerly employed to summon persons to appear in court; an
apparitor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Summons</ent>⟦br⟧
